OL,3,CPolice use new detection technology to
OL,4,Ccrack down on vape spiking
OL,6,FNew vape-spiking detection equipment
OL,7,Fis being used in a crackdown across
OL,8,FLondon, with operations spanning bars,
OL,9,Fclubs and party boats.
OL,11,FChildren as young as 14 were admitted
OL,12,Fto hospital after cannabis products
OL,13,Fwere placed in vapes in a case in
OL,14,Fsouth-east London, the Deputy
OL,15,FAssistant Commissioner at the
OL,16,FMetropolitan Police, Ben Russell, said.
