OL,3,CPolice use new detection technology to
OL,4,Ccrack down on vape spiking
OL,6,FThe technology, which has been used in
OL,7,Fnightclubs, at festivals, concerts and
OL,8,Fschools, allows rapid testing of vapes
OL,9,Fsuspected to contain drugs such as THC
OL,10,For spice, the Met said.
OL,12,FIt is a growing concern for police
OL,13,Fafter reports of vapes being tampered
OL,14,Fwith, often shared between young
OL,15,Fpeople or handed out in social
OL,16,Fsettings, the force added.
