OL,3,CPolice use new detection technology to
OL,4,Ccrack down on vape spiking
OL,6,FThe Met is also using a range of
OL,7,Fmobile drug-testing equipment which
OL,8,Fassist rapid drug identification `
OL,9,Fincluding near infra-red detectors
OL,10,Fthat can test powders and tablets
OL,11,Fsuspected of containing controlled
OL,12,Fdrugs, supported by a mobile phone app.
OL,14,FThe force's Marine Support Unit was
OL,15,Fjoined by Home Office minister Jess
OL,16,FPhillips on Thursday as they led an
OL,17,Foperation patrolling party boats
OL,18,Fembarking and disembarking at
OL,19,FWestminster Pier to identify and
OL,20,Fprevent offending taking place on the
OL,21,Friver.
