OL,3,CPolice use new detection technology to
OL,4,Ccrack down on vape spiking
OL,6,FThe Met received more than 2,000
OL,7,Fallegations of spiking between March
OL,8,F2024 and March 2025, though the force
OL,9,Fbelieves the true scale of the crime
OL,10,Fto be higher due to under-reporting.
OL,12,FThe crime disproportionately affects
OL,13,Fwomen and girls, with 66% of victims
OL,14,Fin August 2025 being female. Offenders
OL,15,Fare most active in and around busy
OL,16,Fnightlife venues, with 17% of reports
OL,17,Flinked to Westminster and the West End.
