OL,3,CPolice use new detection technology to
OL,4,Ccrack down on vape spiking
OL,6,FThe Marine Support Unit led Operation
OL,7,FAlbenga in collaboration with the
OL,8,FMet's licensing teams, drugs dogs,
OL,9,Fsafer transport, and central Violence
OL,10,FAgainst Women and Girls (VAWG) team.
OL,11,FThe operation focused on party boats
OL,12,Falong the Thames, which are popular
OL,13,Fwith students during Freshers Week.
OL,15,FOfficers conducted safety checks,
OL,16,Fengaged with party-goers, and used the
OL,17,Fvape-spiking detection equipment.
