OL,3,CPolice use new detection technology to
OL,4,Ccrack down on vape spiking
OL,6,FThese efforts follow Spiking
OL,7,FIntensification Week, a national
OL,8,Finitiative led by the National Police
OL,9,FChiefs' Council (NPCC) and Home Office.
OL,11,FMr Russell said: "Spiking is an
OL,12,Fabhorrent crime that we are tackling
OL,13,Fhead on, whether it takes place in a
OL,14,Fnightclub, a private venue, or on the
OL,15,FThames. The ongoing trial of new vape-
OL,16,Fspiking detection kits is just one
OL,17,Fexample of how we are innovating to
OL,18,Fget ahead of offenders and better
OL,19,Fprotect the public.
