OL,3,CPolice use new detection technology to
OL,4,Ccrack down on vape spiking
OL,6,F"This is part of our wider commitment
OL,7,Funder the VAWG strategy to protect
OL,8,Fwomen and girls across London. We are
OL,9,Fworking with partners in licensing,
OL,10,Feducation and the night-time economy
OL,11,Fto disrupt offenders, raise awareness
OL,12,Fand, crucially, support victims.
OL,14,F"If you think you've been spiked,
OL,15,Fplease come forward ` being spiked is
OL,16,Fnever your fault, it's always the
OL,17,Ffault of the perpetrator. The sooner
OL,18,Fwe know, the more we can do to support
OL,19,Fyou, collect evidence and stop
OL,20,Fdangerous offenders from targeting
OL,21,Fothers."
