OL,3,CPolice use new detection technology to
OL,4,Ccrack down on vape spiking
OL,6,FHe added that the force has been asked
OL,7,Fto come to schools to test vapes for
OL,8,Fdrugs, saying: "We saw an appalling
OL,9,Fcase in south-east London with a
OL,10,Fnumber of children as young as 14
OL,11,Fyears old hospitalised because
OL,12,Fcannabis products were placed into
OL,13,Ftheir vapes."
OL,15,FMs Phillips said: "As students across
OL,16,Fthe country enjoy Freshers Week, we
OL,17,Fare determined to tackle the vile
OL,18,Fcrime of spiking.
