OL,6,F"That's why we are funding a national
OL,7,FSpiking Intensification Week to raise
OL,8,Fawareness, support police forces to
OL,9,Fuse innovative tactics, and encourage
OL,10,Fvictims to report this crime.
OL,12,F"We are also working with bars, pubs
OL,13,Fand clubs to roll out specialist
OL,14,Ftraining for staff and introducing a
OL,15,Fnew criminal offence for spiking to
OL,16,Fbring more perpetrators to justice."
