OL,6,FShe said she was having lunch in
OL,7,FLondon with friends when she became
OL,8,Funwell and walked to the toilets where
OL,9,Fshe lost consciousness.
OL,11,FMs Gaffka said she was really glad to
OL,12,Fsee the new testing being used by
OL,13,Fpolice, adding: "I got to witness in
OL,14,Fthe briefing room earlier how we're
OL,15,Fnow updating testing, because spiking
OL,16,Fhas moved along, like I was drink-
OL,17,Fspiked, but I'm meeting people that
OL,18,Fare being spiked with needles, being
OL,19,Fspiked with vapes.
